-- GE aircraft unit to buy helicopter lessor Milestone for $1.78 bln
-- By Sagarika Jaisinghani in Bangalore
-- Mon Oct 13, 2014 09:14AM EDT
-- None



Oct 13 (Reuters) - General Electric Co's <GE.N> aircraft leasing unit said it would buy Dublin-based helicopter leasing company Milestone Aviation Group for $1.78 billion.

"The addition of Milestone will deepen our domain expertise in aviation and oil and gas, two critical GE industries," GE Capital Chief Executive Keith Sherin said in a statement on Monday. [ID:nBw5HRY9Ta]